Class Result

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.metrics.common.models.Result
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ServletModelResult

    public class Result
extends Object
    Represents the state of a Metrics Workstation session immediately prior to or following an operation (a query or script).

    mmegliola
